---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import whispurrLogo from "../../assets/whispurr_logo.png";
---

<Layout title="Whispurr">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/projects" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to projects</a>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mb-3">
      <img src={whispurrLogo.src} alt="Whispurr logo" class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
      <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border text-[11px] border-purple-100 text-purple-600 bg-purple-50/60">WIP</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Whispurr</h1>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4 mb-3 md:w-4/5">
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-800">
        <div class="font-semibold mb-1">In one line</div>
        Unfiltered chats. Real privacy. Say anything, share everything—then watch it vanish forever.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-[11px] mb-2">
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Ephemeral chats</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Device-locked privacy</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Emoji vaults</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Burner chats</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Decoy protection</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Zero ads</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4" style="line-height: 2">
      I'm building this because I'm tired of apps that overshare. Every message you send is a tiny revolution against surveillance capitalism.
    </p>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4 mt-3" style="line-height: 2">
      Whispurr lets you speak your mind and connect—no footprints, no judgment. No ads. No tracking. No regrets. Just honest, private conversations.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Core Features</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p><strong>Handshake:</strong> Your messages turn into harmless emoji gibberish if someone looks over your shoulder. Only you can unlock them.</p>
        <p><strong>Vanish Mode:</strong> Send messages that disappear after they're read. No screenshots, no backups, no receipts.</p>
        <p><strong>Decoy Chats:</strong> Set a fake password that opens up a boring, harmless version of your chats. Your real conversations stay hidden.</p>
        <p><strong>Emoji Vaults:</strong> Keep your favorite photos and messages in a private, locked vault. Only you can get in.</p>
        <p><strong>Burner Chats:</strong> Start a chat that deletes itself after a set time. No names, no numbers, no history.</p>
        <p><strong>Device-Locked Privacy:</strong> Your data stays on your phone. No cloud storage, no hidden copies, no leaks.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200">
        <p class="text-sm text-purple-800">
          <strong>Why I'm building this:</strong> This isn't just another app. It's your digital safe space. We're making surveillance capitalism obsolete, one message at a time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">The Problem & Solution</h3>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-red-600 mb-2">What Other Apps Actually Do</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• Harvest your metadata</li>
              <li>• Store your encryption keys</li>
              <li>• Bow to government pressure</li>
              <li>• Sell your attention to advertisers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-green-600 mb-2">What Whispurr Actually Does</h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
              <li>• True end-to-end encryption</li>
              <li>• Zero knowledge: only you can read your messages</li>
              <li>• Device-only storage</li>
              <li>• No ads, no tracking, no surprises</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Technical Approach</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Privacy First</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">End-to-end encryption with zero-knowledge architecture</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">E2E Encryption</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Zero Knowledge</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Device Storage</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">No cloud storage, everything stays on your device</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Local Storage</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">No Cloud</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Ephemeral Design</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Messages that disappear, vaults that self-destruct</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Auto-Delete</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Timers</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Playful UX</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Privacy as performance, anonymity as armor</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Emoji UI</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Animated</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Current Status</h3>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          Whispurr is currently in development. I'm building the core privacy features and working on:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1 list-disc ml-5" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <li>End-to-end encryption implementation</li>
          <li>Emoji curtain and decoy chat systems</li>
          <li>Vanish mode and auto-delete timers</li>
          <li>Device-locked storage architecture</li>
          <li>Playful UI with animated emojis</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="https://whispurr.netlify.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80">Visit App</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">All Projects</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">Ask Questions</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
<Footer />
